.TH TIT 1 "May 2026" "Version 0.1" "Termux Tools"
.SH NAME
tit \- Termux Tools InsTall
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tit
\fIinstall\fR \fI<apk_file>\fR
.br
.B tit
\fIuninstall\fR \fI<package_name>\fR
.br
.B tit
\fIdevices\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBtit\fR is a lightweight tool to install/uninstall Android APKs
from Termux, automatically choosing between \fBpm\fR (on-device)
and \fBadb\fR (from host) based on runtime environment.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
tit install ~/Download/app.apk
tit uninstall com.termux
tit devices
.fi
